title: Cinnamon raisin cake
ingredients: ['4 tablespoons dark brown soft sugar', '4 tablespoons caster sugar', '1/2 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '110g butter, softened', '4 tablespoons caster sugar', '125ml soured cream', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract', '1 egg', '125g plain flour', '1/2 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '1 pinch salt', '50g raisins']
